<topic id='attribute_clinical_classification_code.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: CLINICAL CLASSIFICATION CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A unique clinical classification identifier for a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_coded_clinical_entry">CODED CLINICAL ENTRY</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
This could be 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_opcs_classification_of_interventions_and_procedures">OPCS Classification of Interventions and Procedures</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_opcs_classification_of_interventions_and_procedures">OPCS-4</xref>) codes or 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_international_classification_of_diseases__icd_">International Classification of Diseases (ICD)</xref>
 codes.        </p>
    <p>
See 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_clinical_coding_introduction">Clinical Coding</xref>
 for further information about the types of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_coded_clinical_entry">CODED CLINICAL ENTRIES</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
